    "body": "`priority` should be automatically be assigned through configuration. One configuration should be `fifo` which is essentially the current tx order. The second configuration should be `gasprice`.\r\nIt would be great if there is an additional configuration `manual`, where the user needs to specify a numeric priority with each transaction (but there is a default priority if not specified)\r\n\r\nExample in hardhat : https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/reference/#transaction-ordering ",
